      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "INSPECTION (8) comes here after a speedy win at Geelong over 460m in 25.89. Top win latest and looms as the one to beat again. PAW CARVER (7) turned in a good run last time, finishing in the placings (30.59) at this track in a Mix 6/7 H. Lines up from box 7 for the first time. The form out of his last race has been franked. Expected to be in this for a long way. DOONGALLA PARODY (2) was below best last time finishing fifth at this track, but prior to that had been racing well including a Maiden win two back at Shepparton. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. PAW FORTRESS (4) hit the frame here last start and can sneak into the finish again.",
